{"tid":1763461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俾票政府買水炮車既\"泛民\"派打手係土共背景開既\"連登\"宣傳送頭抗爭，件事真係好好笑","createTime":"2019-11-30T11:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T10:15:54.000Z","uid":241151,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f898427a1d349d974485c0bc4df5006ef76a7f43","tid":1763461,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:00:43.000Z","msg":"同如果有人話容祖兒公開開炮話要搞死佢經理人同楊生有乜分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad9fcb519d35e04e0f0b40a31ba43620be24d7c","tid":1763461,"uid":198590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#241151 - 瀧野由美仔</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span>, 請大家多加注意, 善用不推文回覆！<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>人地學生就打生打死，鄺神都好自得其樂 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YW4Wctv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYW4Wctv.jpg&h=1310c14d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉&hellip;&hellip;唔好問我點解香港抗爭咁多年都係咁失敗，香港人情況仲越來越差<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fhaha.gif&h=20aa0304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fno.gif&h=29da48de&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1714163/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1714163/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>想知乜嘢叫流水式...集會?流水就不可能集合，集合可能是在新屋嶺... - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>想知乜嘢叫流水式...集會?<br />\n流水就不可能集合，集合可能是在新屋嶺...<br />\n會唔會太過 creative, creative 到亂Q咁嚟。<br />\n定你哋較為喜愛嗌D無意思的口號，做無意義的事，好似時代革命，摺紙咁。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1696584/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1696584/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>改口號啦！[香港人！送頭！] - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>香港人！送頭！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1696549/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1696549/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>點呀？之前係咪話過要追究返邊d人，邊d網，邊d團體同傳媒吹市去送頭既？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2b0VZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2b0VZQ.jpg&h=2ac5df0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來係連登x蘋果吹雞<br />\n難怪有哂地點時間表<br />\n鑊鑊都港島，鑊鑊都推人去死<br />\n流人哋嘅血成就自己得票當選！<br />\n泛民蘋果全部都要仆街冚家鏟！<br />\n<br />\n好彩我一早就同班泛民左膠割晒蓆姐，分化實在好！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsmile.gif&h=0b593ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快d回&quot;拉，不分化，不推文回覆啦&quot;<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>香港既和理非從來唔保護勇武，甚至會阻止勇武制服勇武出賣勇武，所以和理非實則係港奸 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>泛民港奸！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"bb1b9d26b54b3c0e62464c3f8106cd9129e0fdb8","tid":1763461,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f898427a1d349d974485c0bc4df5006ef76a7f43","tid":1763461,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:00:43.000Z","msg":"同如果有人話容祖兒公開開炮話要搞死佢經理人同楊生有乜分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"得喇，入黎啦暗共泛民左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5d44756088cbbab62a37d66720b647a66a73d8","tid":1763461,"uid":177213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcPqcay.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcPqcay.png&h=04f028f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2dbf3e3b0f609534d41e6a4300be060b65d711d","tid":1763461,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fa5d44756088cbbab62a37d66720b647a66a73d8","tid":1763461,"uid":177213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcPqcay.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcPqcay.png&h=04f028f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"ci